title: At Least Don't Lie
description:
pay those voices no mind I'm 
too busy tryna fly so i 

alright 
the devil better here me now
I got no time to fear and i got zero doubt
I know how to hear the holy spirits sound
yall gone rub off and make me lose my ground 
yalls self doubts contagious
yall having conversations
vain imaginations
I beg you
don't give into temptations
I ain't tripping
I ain't giving up 
a single inch man
I really live this
this is real as it gets to me
so don't matter what nobody says to me
I see what we're sacrificing
the assonine gaslighting
pacify the screaming child
but the spoiled brat don't have to like it
your too lost in these thoughts
the devil haunts your distraught
it's not real it's all talk
let time tell and God be God
dip the sword into the fire
let the embers heat the iron
either make him king as he desires
or quit waisting time and crucify him
cuz we ain't got all day 
yall no work and all play
I'm like that damn voice that won't go away
thinking all the things your afraid to say
crippled by the fear to criticize
you sit in a jail and rot away
I've herd the devils words but I ain't got space to give that shit the time of day 

holy spirits here now
ain't no time for self doubt

it's unethical to allow the media to terrorize the citzens
it's unethical to make a man with dementia to be president
it's inethical to close the churches and bankrupt small businesses
while the liquor stores stay open and criminals are let out of prison
it's unethical to allow peoples private data collected
it's unethical to leverage a black or trans person's experience
it unethical to lock people in their homes
push a v@x!ne down their throat
then villianize em when they dont

these people are morally bankrupt
these people who rule you
they are morally and ethically and spiritually bankrupt
 
hey there pastor
I'm watching you stand there at the pulpit all masked up
saying Jesus is the answer
if you don't speak up
who does
yes God is judge but dont you speak for  him bruh

devil do your worst
but you will not defeat the church

whose gonna break the silence
as we watch our children tossed to the den of lions
lockdowns don't work according to science
but lockdowns work great  
when creating compliance
don't back down dont bow to this twisted mind virus
it's a frog in a pot and the water has got
to a level so high unless we cause it to stop
say enough is enough
in the name of my God
take my axe to the root cuz we're chopping it off 

talk all you want 
I only fear God
so your not worth my time if you bought into this farce
I ain't tryna hate I'm just saying cmon
even if I do it wrong
imma speak my truth that's all I got
I dont claim to be perfect
listen none of us are
but these immoral people will just keep taking control 
until righteous men do what's right and tell the principality no
